{"tid":611853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑪麗女病人院內感染丙型肝炎死亡 疑經抽血輔助器傳播","createTime":"2018-03-31T12:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T03:59:53.000Z","uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd964c06301b56d1555cb96f7d6ebbc78389eed","tid":611853,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%91%AA%E9%BA%97%E5%A5%B3%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E4%B8%99%E5%9E%8B%E8%82%9D%E7%82%8E%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E7%96%91%E7%B6%93%E6%8A%BD%E8%A1%80%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E5%99%A8%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD-093200552.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2591%25AA%25E9%25BA%2597%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E4%25B8%2599%25E5%259E%258B%25E8%2582%259D%25E7%2582%258E%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%25BC%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2592%25AD-093200552.html&d=y4chBs1IqmZRMRvYqKKP0CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c2944e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%91%AA%E9%BA%97%E5%A5%B3%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E4%B8%99%E5%9E%8B%E8%82%9D%E7%82%8E%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E7%96%91%E7%B6%93%E6%8A%BD%E8%A1%80%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E5%99%A8%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD-093200552.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】瑪麗醫院發生院內感染丙型肝炎個案！一名53歲患有多囊性肝病的女病人，接受肝臟移植後肝功能出現不正常，至去年12月甲多重器官衰竭死亡，院方懷疑病人在在使用可重用的抽血輔助器後受感染。<br />\n<br />\n港大微生學系講座教授袁國勇表示，病人前年10月接受肝移植，去年9月發現肝功能不正常，至去年12月因多重器官功能衰竭死亡。院方經調查後，發現病人在進行移植前並無任何高風險因素，包括沒有紋身、無濫藥，亦沒有進行不安全性行為等，而有關病毒亦非捐贈者感染。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇指，院方經進一步調查後，發現病人入住的病房中，其中一名濫藥病人患有丙型肝炎，懷疑病人在接受抽血時受感染。院方其後在病房一個可重用的抽血輔助器中，發現丙型肝炎病毒。<br />\n<br />\n他續說，今次是首次發現，抽血時針頭上的病毒會沾上抽血輔助器，導致丙型肝炎傳播，形容個案是不尋常。<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 17:06<br />\n<br />\n更新時間 17:32<br />\n<br />\n這就是香港了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ede7e69179ff8fe0ea5c54cd194949c6d2eccb0","tid":611853,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b7f4d42a5911fca3ffd9f8739eaf7a468e78b2f","tid":611853,"uid":47359,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"2ede7e69179ff8fe0ea5c54cd194949c6d2eccb0","tid":611853,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你住深圳?"},{"pid":"be978e924f33fb4fd5332e54d74f091bc621156e","tid":611853,"uid":83251,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2ede7e69179ff8fe0ea5c54cd194949c6d2eccb0","tid":611853,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20141118/00176_048.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141118%2F00176_048.html&d=y4chBs1IqmZRMRvYqKKP0CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=697ca5e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20141118/00176_048.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2014 11 18<br />\n港料四年後「零丙肝」<br />\n可致肝硬化的丙型肝炎（丙肝）不容忽視，最新「三合一」療法在傳統藥物組合外，加入蛋白酶抑制劑，阻病毒複製，令治愈率升至八成。新藥費用高達約三十萬元，公院今年七月將新藥納藥物名冊，為使用傳統藥物無效的患者帶來喜訊，每年至少四十人可免費接受新治療。有肝臟科專家預期，丙肝患者全部接受新一代治療，本港最快四年後成為全球首個「零丙肝」城市。<br />\n<br />\n說好了的零丙肝呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php4Ic3tg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%